WEBVTT

00:02:28.339 --> 00:02:30.073
"This is my dumpling way."

00:02:31.292 --> 00:02:33.775
GÄo's team was also puzzled.

00:02:34.252 --> 00:02:37.474
In the first three months,
the sales fluctuated,

00:02:37.498 --> 00:02:39.950
some even dropped by 20 percent.

00:02:39.974 --> 00:02:41.847
But GÄo didn't blink.

00:02:42.704 --> 00:02:47.283
The regional heads had to learn new skills
while still doing their job.

00:02:47.307 --> 00:02:50.712
Things like what kinds of dumplings
can be sold online,

00:02:50.736 --> 00:02:53.553
how to digitalize their supply chain.

00:02:54.569 --> 00:02:56.403
After the transition period,

00:02:56.427 --> 00:02:58.133
something magical happened.

00:02:58.157 --> 00:02:59.696
The sales came back.

00:02:59.720 --> 00:03:01.022
One year later,